These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, trike
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Beverage   | fanta  | coffee |
| Transport     | trike | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, light-blue
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Color   | aquamarine | light-blue |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different games are played: canasta, bridge
There 2 different types of food: orange, spinach
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Game   | bridge | canasta   |
| Food       | spinach  | orange |

 #################################

 
